    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped... i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s still oozing a bit but it’s not like spraying blood or anything. i dont really want to go to the hospital if i dont have to, do u think i can just put some organic honey on it and bandage it up? i heard that helps things heal faster",
