      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not really gaping or anything, just kinda wide. but like, if i do the honey thing, do i need to use any antiseptic first? i dont want to make it sting too much if i can avoid it. would just the honey be enough to keep it clean and stop it from getting infected?",
